CustomField.inlineHelpText:
This field stores the description of the form.

For file upload forms you can use these tags in your description:
{NumberOfFiles}
{NumberOfFilesAtOnce}
{MaxIndividualFileSizeMB}
{AllowedExtensions}
{HeightMinimumPixels}
{HeightMaximumPixels}
{WidthMinimumPixels}
{WidthMaximumPixels}
